Package kinectThreads

Interface Summary
IKinectAbsoluteSpaceForATimeListener Must be implemented by all classes that want to get and deal with KinectAbsoluteSpaceForATime events.
IKinectPoseListener Must be implemented by all classes that want to get and deal with the Kinect Pose events.
IKinectTotalSpaceTravelledForATimeListener Must be implemented by all classes that want to get and deal with KinectTotalSpaceTravelledForATime events.
IKinectUserMovementListener Must be implemented by all classes that want to get and deal with the Kinect Pose events.
 

Class Summary
KinectAbsoluteSpaceForATime This class implements the logic to calculate the space that exists between the initial and final position of a given joint of a given user when a given time expires.
KinectAbsoluteSpaceForATimeEvent  
KinectEnhancedSkeletonLauncher This class provides enhanced functionalities to the KinectSkeletonLauncher class like the socket-based data sending.
KinectPoseManager This class re-launches the KinectSkeleton events so that they can be received and processed as KinectPoses.
KinectTilt  
KinectTotalSpaceTravelledForATime This class implements the logic to calculate the space that a given user's joint has gone over throughout a given time.
KinectTotalSpaceTravelledForATimeEvent  
 

Enum Summary
KinectPoseEnum This enum lists all the different poses that can be recognised by the Kinect.
KinectUserActionEnum This enum lists all the different actions that the games need about the user.
